data.title: All Inductees
data.meta_description: Join us as we congratulate our team, coach/staff, and individual inductees!
data.text:
Since its founding in 1995, the William C. Ackmann Memorial Athletic Hall of Fame has served to honor the most celebrated athletes of Concordia University Wisconsin. Each year we proudly induct exceptional CUW faculty, staff, students or alumni into the Hall of Fame for their contributions to CUW Athletics Department.
